title: Blind - Video Days [1991][skateboarding] DVDrip.avi
description:
BLIND - VIDEO DAYS (1991)

classic skate film now on DVD re-issue.
starring
Mark Gonzales, Jason Lee, Guy Mariano, Rudy Johnson and Jordan Richter.

if you skate, then it's mandatory to watch this video.
this a great video from the street skating revolution happening just after
the death of 80's vert skating.
alot of people think it started with 1989's H-Street - Hokus Pokus;
well maybe it might have, but this video seems to get mentioned
more than any other.

Gonzales' style, Jason Lee's 360 flips, Mariano's lines, Rudy's tech and
Richter's miniramp attack... it never gets old.

and, yeah, that's Jason Lee, the famous actor, for those who care.
Mallrats, Enemy of the State, Almost Famous,
Alvin and the Chipmunks... alotta flicks.
that dude even did voice work in "The Incredibles". hahaha
yessssir.



bookmark highateus, check for goods and please help SEED.
thanks
